Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} from reaching its peak.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.70,0:08:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} There the bell has{\i0}\N{\i1} remained... until now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.91,0:08:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Scale Mt. Everhoof.\NBring me back my bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.71,0:08:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha! The ease of this\Ntask is laughable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it sounded easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Scale the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Retrieve Grogar's bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.23,0:08:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Together! I drew\Nup a detailed plan
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,with several visual\Naides to show how we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:08:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,ditch each other\Nand do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe when I'm waiting\Nfor them at the top,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.01,0:09:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,then they'll appreciate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [music intensifies] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,As if anything on this\Nmountain is scarier than I.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.01,0:09:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.92,0:09:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ptui!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Halt! Who goes there? A pony!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There ain't been\Nponies round here in
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I-don't-know-how-many moons!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.87,0:10:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, golly, good sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a poor lost\Npony looking for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't fret li'l filly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ol' Rusty Bucket\Nhere, at yer service!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad\NI found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I need help getting to\Nthe top of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh. No can do, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,WHY NOT!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh! Not so loud! This here's\Navalanche territory!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the guardian of\Nthis here mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my job to keep\Nponies from heading up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at the top\Nbut dangerous snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,dangerous ice, and\Ndangerous wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It must get lonely\Nall by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I could be\Nyour... friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.54,0:10:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I'd love a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.01,0:10:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So now that we\Nare friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you could help me\Nup the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. A real friend wouldn't\Nask me to do something
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.72,0:10:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not supposed to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Says so right here in the\Njournal of friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:11:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,written by Twilight\NSparkle and {\i1}her{\i0} friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,ARE! YOU! KIDDING ME!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sshhhhhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to\Nbe friends anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.55,0:11:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.68,0:11:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. Not that\Nway neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I TRIED being NICE.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shhhhh. Now just calm\Ndown there, filly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponies are supposed to\Ndo what I ask them to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like MY thing, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.65,0:12:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently I don't\Nneed anypony else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.85,0:13:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not. Funny. Tirek!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't make it to the\Ntop? Surprise surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't make it\Nto the top either!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't try to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It took about five\Nminutes to deduce
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.97,0:13:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that Grogar was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,None of us could\Nmake it up alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So rather than subject\Nmyself to the elements,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to let you\Ntwo face the danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,take what you learned and\Nuse it to my advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.92,0:13:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I put up with your "I'm\Nsmarter than you" attitude
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,in Tartarus! But\NI'm over it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of you\Ntrying to manipulate me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.56,0:13:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,with that insincere\Nsyrupy sweetness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,At least now we can\Nsee the real you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is NOT the real me!\NI'm cute and LOVABLE!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! No, you're not. You're\Nannoying and you snore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:14:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not snore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,At least I don't talk to\Nmy gram-gram in {\i1}my{\i0} sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you DARE bring\NGram-Gram into this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick! It's\Ndistracted! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmmm. So much love...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't eaten\Nthis well in {\i1}ages{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[gag] So gross...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so we're clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't save you\Nbecause I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it because...\NBecause I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Neeeeeed us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:14:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:15:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Clearly, I was\Nright to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Now tell me everything\Nyou learned today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.24,0:15:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave nothing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you already\Ndrain it of love?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.48,0:15:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I always save a little\Nfor the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You cocoon all of\Nyour... meals?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.15,0:15:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.30,0:15:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you pony-napped\NTwilight and the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.66,0:15:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you cocooned them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Until that sow\NStarlight Glimmer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,freed them, corrupted my\Nsubjects, and stole my hive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Those ponies have weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I used that turncoat Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.27,0:15:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Tricked him into\Nhelping me capture his
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,so called "friends".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.81,0:15:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Discord was really something\Nuntil friendship ruined him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've seen\NTwilight's face
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,when her friends appeared\Nin bubbles around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She was all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:16:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She's SO stressed\Nout all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When I posed as her\Nformer foal-sitter,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.43,0:16:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she was\Ngoing to implode!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could\Nhave seen her face
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,when I nearly erased all\Nthe magic from Equestria...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,ALL magic was a little\Nexcessive, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.48,0:16:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Meh. I think big.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.71,0:16:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, it would've\Nbeen worth it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,just to see Twilight and\Nher friends bow down to ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, it would. Who\Nwouldn't love to see
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.79,0:16:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,those prissy ponies realize\Nthey've lost everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.79,0:16:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a pathetic pony princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.36,0:16:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a detailed list of\Nall the ways I'm a failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, working with you two
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,may not be the worst thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm. Perhaps... as long as it results
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.25,0:16:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in the complete\Ndestruction of our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.02,0:16:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have\Nit any other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.65,0:16:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Do the "pathetic\Nprincess" thing again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.75,0:18:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[zap] Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[zap] Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you absorb it\Nand make it go away?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only absorb magic\Nfrom living beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Like her..?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.67,0:18:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Betrayal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Not betrayal. Teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If Tirek absorbs your energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,he might be strong\Nenough to break through.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And then..?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... he\Ngives it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.65,0:18:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mhm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I know you won't\Ntake my magic and leave me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Would we do\Nthat to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Normally\Nyes, we would.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.66,0:18:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you\Nyour magic back...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So. Much. Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.28,0:19:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not big enough for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it open or I'll\Nbe trapped forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Would that be so terrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't... hold.... much longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,HURRY!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I... wasn't sure you were\Ngoing to give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither was I. But working\Ntogether seemed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,smarter than to\Ncontinue fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.76,0:19:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,When we helped each other,\Nit felt better somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't felt like this\Nsince before I lost my hive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.43,0:19:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Having others who will\Nbe there for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.73,0:20:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,is pleasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All of these years...\Ntaking power from ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When you use your\Npower to help others...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.... it feels....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.45,0:20:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The magic of {\i1}friendship{\i0}\Nis like a disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,An infection that spreads\Nto those around you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.26,0:20:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I watched it\Ninfect my hive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I will NOT let it get ME!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.69,0:20:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Same!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.36,0:20:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Grogar said we\Nhave to work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.20,0:20:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Grogar is too powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.53,0:20:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Something must be\Ndone about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let Grogar think we're\Nhis loyal servants.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, we'll\Nhatch our own plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.15,0:20:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooo. I love a good\Nbackstabbing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.98,0:20:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, we can go back
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to trying to..\Ndestroy each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, what\Ndo we do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:21:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You failed to\Nretrieve the BELL?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry,\NAlmighty Grogar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We worked together\Nas you asked!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We just aren't as\Npowerful as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.61,0:21:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,At least you finally\Ndid as you were told
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and worked together.
